    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Find \u2014 Truly Mint Condition! \ud83c\udf1f If you've been searching for a vehicle that feels and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor, your search is over! This car is in absolutely pristine condition \u2014 the exterior is flawless, with a gleaming finish free of scratches, dents, or blemishes. Step inside and you'll find an interior that's equally immaculate: spotless upholstery, clean surfaces throughout, and everything working exactly as it should. Under the hood, this car has been meticulously maintained and is ready to perform at its best. Opportunities like this don't come along often \u2014 a vehicle in this kind of condition is truly a cut above. Come see it for yourself and experience the difference mint condition really makes!",
      "price": 46000.0,
