    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in fair condition, and I want to be upfront about what that means. The car is mechanically functional and will get you where you need to go, but it does show its age and use. The exterior has visible wear \u2014 expect some paint fading, minor dents, and surface scratches that are noticeable upon close inspection. The interior is similarly worn, with scuffed surfaces, some upholstery wear, and minor trim pieces that may need attention. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance work in the near term \u2014 think of it as a car that needs a little love rather than one that's ready to go without any investment. This is an honest, budget-friendly option for a buyer who is handy, doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections, or simply needs reliable basic transportation without paying for a pristine example.",
      "price": 20000.0,
